&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Dementia and Mental Health Specialist Nurse &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The candidate should have a passion to want to improve Dementia and delirium care for patients within a quick paced elective organisation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Have the knowledge and drive to support the trust to write its dementia strategy and deliverer the objectives within the strategy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Ensuring appropriate training for staff – provision and delivery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Ensuring appropriate support for patients through identification, assessment and sign posting to appropriate services for follow on care.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
